Source-Makefile: feeds/packages/libs/libmbus/Makefile
Package: libmbus
Version: 0.7.0-1
Depends: +libc +USE_EGLIBC:librt +USE_EGLIBC:libpthread 
Menu-Depends: 
Provides: 
Section: libs
Category: Libraries
Title: libmbus
Maintainer: OpenWrt Developers Team <openwrt-devel@openwrt.org>
Source: libmbus-0.7.0.tar.gz
Type: ipkg
Description:     libmbus is an open source M-bus (Meter-Bus) library.
  The Meter-Bus is a standard for reading out meter data from
  electricity meters, heat meters, gas meters, etc.

  This package contains the M-bus shared library, used by other programs.
http://www.freescada.com/libmbus/
OpenWrt Developers Team <openwrt-devel@openwrt.org>
@@

Package: mbus-serial
Version: 0.7.0-1
Depends: +libc +USE_EGLIBC:librt +USE_EGLIBC:libpthread +libmbus
Menu-Depends: 
Provides: 
Section: utils
Category: Utilities
Title: mbus-tools (serial)
Maintainer: OpenWrt Developers Team <openwrt-devel@openwrt.org>
Source: libmbus-0.7.0.tar.gz
Type: ipkg
Description:     libmbus is an open source M-bus (Meter-Bus) library.
  The Meter-Bus is a standard for reading out meter data from
  electricity meters, heat meters, gas meters, etc.

  This package contains command line tools for scanning the M-bus
  and retrieving data from meters which are connected through a
  serial (e.g. RS232) interface.
http://www.freescada.com/libmbus/
OpenWrt Developers Team <openwrt-devel@openwrt.org>
@@

Package: mbus-tcp
Version: 0.7.0-1
Depends: +libc +USE_EGLIBC:librt +USE_EGLIBC:libpthread +libmbus
Menu-Depends: 
Provides: 
Section: utils
Category: Utilities
Title: mbus-tools (tcp)
Maintainer: OpenWrt Developers Team <openwrt-devel@openwrt.org>
Source: libmbus-0.7.0.tar.gz
Type: ipkg
Description:     libmbus is an open source M-bus (Meter-Bus) library.
  The Meter-Bus is a standard for reading out meter data from
  electricity meters, heat meters, gas meters, etc.

  This package contains command line tools for scanning the M-bus
  and retrieving data from meters which are accessible through
  M-bus gateways via TCP.
http://www.freescada.com/libmbus/
OpenWrt Developers Team <openwrt-devel@openwrt.org>
